laboratory_examinations.findings: Basal LH 15.7 IU/liter, Peak LH 68.8 IU/liter; Basal FSH 15.5 IU/liter, Peak FSH 34.7 IU/liter; Basal testosterone 9.6 nmol/liter, Peak testosterone 32.3 nmol/liter.
Mutation identified: Arg629Trp; CAG repeats = 29 (normal range 11-31).
Mutant AR transactivation was 40% higher than wild type at the highest DHT concentration tested; no statistically significant difference.
